column5: I have a buddy whos looking for two sets of points for a 1979 moto ski mirage 300 with a 294cc rotax motor.  Im having a hard time finding them, anyone got any "connections"?
Remind me on Monday TJ and I will check with the guys to see if we have some in stock.
TJ, Im storing a 79 citation in my garage for a friend who thinks it may get trashed by years end. Would the "points" be the same?
TJ if Bernie can't help you let me know I have a friend who has bought a ton of dealer old stock over the years and may have them.
TJ... just hit my link for buy it now.. $8.95 and $2.65 postage !
